===========================| Test Case #2 |=============================
========================================================================

Summary:
    Sing in

Precondition:
    - Open a Firefox
    - Will make sure that you does not have account
    - You are still on stay in "Учет запчастей"

STR:
    1. Click a link "Зарегистрироваться"
    2. Popup will appear "Регистрация" with input fields
    3. Input text area a "Имя", "Фалилию", "возраст",
     "Email", "номер мобильного"
    4. Click "Регистрация"

ER:
    We must can see the message "Вы зарегистрированы"
    Log in to your account

Post condition:
    1. Click into avatar in a upper right side "Student"
    2. Click a button "Выход"
    3. Close a Firebox browser

========================================================================
===========================| Test Case #3 |=============================
========================================================================

Summary:
    Add a new deal to list

Precondition:
    Open a Firefox

STR:
    1.  Go to url "http://v3.test.itpmgroup.com"
    2.  Enter Login -> "Student"
    3.  Enter password -> "909090"
    4.  Click button "Вход"
    5.  Click on the left SideBar by link "Deal"
    6.  Click right "+" (popup "Add")
    7.  Change "Deal Date" to "08-мая-2020-06-05"
    8.  Change "Тип сделки" to "мошеничество"
    9.  Change "Покупатель" to "OAO "МММ"
    10. Change "Я, Олег Ляшко"
    11. Click button "Создать"

ER:
    We need to see "Сделки => Список"
    08.05.2020 06:05 мошеничество ОАО "МММ" Я, Олег Ляшко

Post condition:
    1.  Scroll down to list
    2.  Click "Deal Date" to "08-мая-2020-06-05"
    3.  Change "Тип сделки" to "мошеничество"
    4.  Click button "Удалить"

ER:
    We need to see "Сделки => Список" with out
    08.05.2020 06:05 мошеничество ОАО "МММ" Я, Олег Ляшко

Post condition:
    1. Click into avatar in a upper right side "Student"
    2. Click a button "Выход"
    3. Close a Firebox browser

