===========================| Test Case #5 |=============================
========================================================================

Summary:
    Add to new side a deal

Precondition:
    Open a Firefox

STR Before:
    1.  Go on the url "http://v3.test.itpmgroup.com"
    2.  Insert a text area Login -> 'Student'
    3.  Insert a text area Password -> '909090'
    4.  Click button "Вход"
    5.  Click on the left SideBar by link "Deal"
    6.  Click button "Словари"
    7.  Select a drop down "Стороны сделок" and click selected
    8.  Click button "+"
    9.  Insert to text area "Pro cust name" -> "Чепуха Олексеевич"
    10. Insert to text area "Pro cust address" -> "Pro cust address"
    11. Insert to text area "Pro cust phone" -> "09889900451"
    12. Click checkbox "Private person" -> enabled
    13. Click "Создать"

ER:
    We will see a create a new line of List Deal
    Чепуха Олексеевич  Свиридова 23б кв.12    09889900451

Post condition:
    1. Click into avatar in a upper right side "Student"
    2. Click a button "Выход"
    3. Close a Firebox browser

